<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <title>Rainbow Latin Reader - Index</title>
        
        <style>
            body {
                background-color: rgb(10, 17, 27);
                color: #c9cfd6;
                padding: 0em;
                margin: 0em;
                font-size: calc(0.9vw + 0.5vh + 4px);
            }

            div.content {
                padding: 0em;
                padding-top: 1em;
                padding-bottom: 1em;
                position: relative;
                background-color: rgb(13, 34, 53);
                width: 40em;
                left: calc(50% - 20em);
            }

            div.content h1 {
                margin-top: 0em;
                padding: 0.3em;
                padding-left: 1em;
                font-size: 1.5em;
                background-color: #18466f;
            }

            div.content h2 {
                font-size: 1.2em;
                padding: 0.2em;
                padding-left: 1em;
                background-color: #18466f;
                color: #bac0c6;
            }

            div.content h3 {
                font-size: 1.1em;
                margin-bottom: 0.1em;
                padding: 0.2em;
                padding-left: 1em;
            }

            div.content p {
                font-size: 1em;
                padding-left: 1em;
                padding-right: 1em;
            }

            div.content ol {
                padding-left: 5em;
            }

            div.content ul {
                padding-left: 3em;
                padding-right: 2em;
            }

            div.content li {
                font-size: 1em;
            }

            div.content a {
                color: #c9cfd6;
            }

            div.content a:hover {
                color: white;
            }

            /*
                Tables
            */
            div.content table {
                border-collapse: collapse;
                width: 39em;
                margin-left: 0.5em;
            }

            div.content .header td {
                background-color: #0e1926;
            }

            div.content td {
                border: 1px solid #434f5e;
                padding: 0.3em;
                font-size: 1em;
            }

            div.content td.min {
                width: 1%;
            }
        </style>
    </head>

    <body>
        <div class="content">
            <h1>Welcome to Rainbow Latin Reader!</h1>

            <p>This site provides dual-language Latin-English documents with a built-in dictionary.
                You can find the list of currently available works below. Please note that their number will be
                continuously increasing in the future.</p>
            
            <ol>
                <li><a href="#document-index">Document Index</a></li>
                <li><a href="#credits">Credits</a></li>
                <li><a href="#useful-links">Useful links</a></li>
            </ol>

            <a name="document-index"></a>
            <h2>1. Document Index</h2>

            {{#each index}}
                <h3>{{author}}</h3>

                <table>
                    <tr class="header">
                        <td>Title / Link</td>
                        <td class="min">Perseus&nbsp;code</td>
                        <td class="min">Latin&nbsp;word&nbsp;count</td>
                    </tr>

                    {{#each works}}
                        <tr>
                            <td><a href="{{link}}">{{title}}</a></td>
                            <td class="min">{{perseus_code}}</td>
                            <td class="min">{{word_count}}</td>
                        </tr>
                    {{/each}}
                </table>
            {{/each}}

            <a name="credits"></a>
            <h2>2. Credits</h2>

            <p>Rainbow Latin Reader was created by <a href="https://github.com/bolner" target="_blank">Tamas Bolner</a>
                and published under the <a href="http://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0" target="_blank">Apache License</a>
                (Copyright 2024). It is based on the following 3 projects:</p>

            <ul>
                <li><a href="https://github.com/PerseusDL/canonical-latinLit" target="_blank">Perseus Canonical Latin literature</a></li>
                <li><a href="https://mk270.github.io/whitakers-words/dictionary.html" target="_blank">Whitaker's Words</a>.</li>
                <li><a href="https://github.com/lascivaroma/latin-lemmatized-texts" target="_blank">Lemmatized Latin texts by Thibault Cl√©rice et al.</a></li>
            </ul>
            
            <a name="useful-links"></a>
            <h2>3. Useful links</h2>

            <ul>
                <li><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9ufyqLxwcEE" target="_blank">Introductory video</a> for this project.</li>
                <li>You can download <a href="https://bolner.de/rainbow-latin-reader.zip" target="_blank">all documents in a ZIP file</a>
                    and open them on a tablet or desktop PC without network connection.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>
